{{Infobox film | name = Severus Snape and the Marauders | image = File:Severus Snape and the Marauders.jpg | alt = Severus Snape and the Marauders | caption = Official release poster | director = Justin Zagri | producer = Liana Minassian | writer = Justin Zagri | starring = {{Plainlist| * [[Mick Ignis]] * [[Garrett Schweighauser]] * Kevin Allen * Paul Stanko * Zachary David * Dani Jae }} | music = Alexander Arntzen | cinematography = John Hafner | editing = Justin Zagri | studio = Broad Strokes | distributor = [[New Line Cinema]] | released = {{film date|2016|03|01}} | runtime = 23 minutes | country = United States | language = English | image_size = | border = }}
'''''Severus Snape and the Marauders''''' is a 2016 American [[short film]] written by director Justin Zagri, based on ''[[Harry Potter]]'' characters by [[J. K. Rowling]]. It officially premiered<ref name="Harry Potter Fan Film">{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EmsntGGjxiw/ | title = Severus Snape and the Marauders| work = youtube.com}}</ref> on March 1, 2016 at the [[Youtube]] channel Broad Strokes Productions.<ref name="Broad Strokes">{{cite web| url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCh9oISfvaQw3clITyi0rzJw/ | title = Broad Strokes Productions| work = youtube.com}}</ref> The fan film caught the attention of [[BuzzFeed]],<ref name="BuzzFeed">{{cite web| url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/alivelez/severus-snape-and-the-marauders | title = This Harry Potter Fan Film Is The Prequel We All Need And Deserve | work = buzzfeed.com}}</ref> ''[[Entertainment Weekly]]'',<ref name="Entertainment Weekly">{{cite web| url=http://ew.com/article/2016/03/24/fan-made-harry-potter-prequel/ | title = Harry Potter prequel: Fan-made video surfaces | work = ew.com}}</ref> ''[[Time (magazine)|Time]]'',<ref name="Time">{{cite web| url=http://time.com/4271941/watch-harry-potter-prequel/ | title = This Fan-Made Harry Potter Prequel Is Stunning | work = time.com}}</ref> ''[[Elite Daily]]'',<ref name="Elite Daily">{{cite web| url=http://elitedaily.com/entertainment/fan-made-harry-potter-prequel/1434408/ | title = This Fan Made His Own ‘Harry Potter’ Prequel And It’s Absolutely Incredible | work = elitedaily.com}}</ref> ''[[Business Insider]]'',<ref name="Business Insider">{{cite web| url=http://www.businessinsider.com/fan-made-harry-potter-prequel-2016-3/ | title = This fan-made Harry Potter movie has surprisingly convincing special effects | work = businessinsider.com}}</ref> ''[[The Huffington Post]]'',<ref name="The Huffington Post">{{cite web| url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/this-harry-potter-prequel-breathes-new-life-into-james-potter-and-severus-snapes-backstory_us_56f55c45e4b0143a9b48072c/ | title = This ‘Harry Potter’ Prequel Breathes New Life Into James Potter And Severus Snape’s Backstory | work = huffingtonpost.com}}</ref> [[IGN]],<ref name="IGN">{{cite web| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/03/24/cool-harry-potter-fan-film-is-a-severus-snape-prequel | title = COOL HARRY POTTER FAN FILM IS A SEVERUS SNAPE PREQUEL | work = ign.com}}</ref> ''[[Seventeen (American magazine)|Seventeen]]'',<ref name="Seventeen">{{cite web| url=http://www.seventeen.com/celebrity/movies-tv/news/a39141/this-fan-made-harry-potter-movie-about-young-snape-and-the-marauders-is-the-hp-prequel-we-deserve/ | title = This Fan-Made "Harry Potter" Prequel About the End of Lily Potter and Snape's Friendship is Heartbreaking | work = seventeen.com}}</ref> [[Moviepilot]],<ref name="Movie Pilot">{{cite web | url=http://moviepilot.com/posts/3384856/ | title=Fan-Made Short 'Severus Snape and The Marauders' Will Show the Pre-Potter World We've All Been Waiting For | work=moviepilot.com | access-date=2017-01-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513223558/http://moviepilot.com/posts/3384856# | archive-date=2016-05-13 | dead-url=yes | df= }}</ref> [[MTV]],<ref name="MTV">{{cite web| url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2799256/harry-potter-prequel-severus-snape-marauders/ | title = Severus Snape and the Marauders is The Harry Potter Prequel You've Been Waiting For | work = MTV}}</ref> [[BBC America]],<ref name="BBC America">{{cite web| url=http://www.bbcamerica.com/anglophenia/2015/07/watch-harry-potter-fan-film-severus-snape-and-the-marauders | title = WATCH: Harry Potter Fan Film 'Severus Snape and the Marauders' | work = bbcamerica.com}}</ref> [[PopSugar]],<ref name="PopSugar">{{cite web| url=http://www.popsugar.com/tech/Harry-Potter-Marauders-Fan-Film-40442413 | title = FINALLY! There's a Harry Potter Movie About Snape and the Marauders' | work = popsugar.com}}</ref> ''[[The Independent]]'',<ref name="The Independent">{{cite web| url=https://www.independent.co